{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 17,
  "title": "第十七章（淳風）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "太上，下知有之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "其次，親之譽之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "其次畏之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "其次侮之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "信不足焉，﹝有不信焉﹞。"
    },
    {
      "text": "猶兮其貴言。"
    },
    {
      "text": "功成事遂，"
    },
    {
      "text": "百姓皆謂我自然。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "太上，謂太古無名之君。 下知有之者，下知上有君，而不臣事，質朴也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其德可見，恩惠可稱，故親愛而譽之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "設刑法以治之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "禁多令煩，不可歸誠，故欺侮之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "君信不足於下，下則應之以不信，而欺其君也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "說太上之君，舉事猶，貴重於言，恐離道失自然也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂天下太平也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "百姓不知君上之德淳厚，反以為己自當然也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
